Features: Add tasks with a name, category, priority, and hours.
Statistics: Completed/Total/Hours/Progress Percentage
Points: Points are calculated using the formula priority * hours
Filtering: All/Active/Completed
Delete tasks
Priority chips with mini-statistics
Add tasks by pressing Enter

Stack:
1) React 18 - UI
2) Vite 5 - builder
3) CSS - custom styles (without UI libraries)
4) Space Mono - font (Google Fonts)
